\n時代革命"},{"pid":"e481c4451c92e06fbf07a179c5bec6bf88175114","tid":1360504,"uid":41216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:12:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cf29de5a617ca2ea02d01e137e2e9c60f7fefad","tid":1360504,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"(突發) 有人邀請鄉事派參加元朗727遊行!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361593</a><br />\n<br />\n講得好好, 所以我搵左佢地鄉事派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}